Nutrient data for: MIRABELL MOZART CHOCOLATE PIECES MILK WITH MARZIPAN FILLING, UNPREPARED, GTIN: 07622200004669

Ingredients: Sugar, cocoa mass, vegetable fat (palm), HAZELNUTS, cocoa butter, whey powder (from MILK), ALMONDS, skimmed MILK powder, invert sugar syrup, MILK fat, humectant (sorbitols), fat-reduced cocoa powder, lactose (from MILK), emulsifiers (SOYA lecithin, sunflower lecithin), PISTACHIOS, cherry liqueur (contains alcohol), flavourings, cherry concentrate, stabilizer (invertase), whole MILK powder.Milk chocolate contains: cocoa solids: 35% minimum.
